ize: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjI2NDQ1NA==&amp;mid=2652591230&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e2104e81092acf1a1c9c6bc6497251bd&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LJ-Hl4IlN2vxzIGKXTKEGQ\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LJ-Hl4IlN2vxzIGKXTKEGQ</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在AI浪潮下，百度搜索通过三大层面全面 AI 化：重塑底层系统以建立“超级大脑”猎户座 AI 引擎、改进产品交互使机器更懂人且更主动、以及扩展搜索边界实现从找答案到创作的跨越。该转型不仅提升信息检索与任务执行的智能化，还推动多模态创作、内容生成和创作者生态的发展，旨在让搜索成为解决问题、表达情感与激发创意的综合搭子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968349\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7014314928425358\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"978\" width=\"978\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b65278e1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TRia2ib69CurGVFVGkGDUoxQO9ze7VzUmwXn1K2HezAgJRPHc9x7nov01bjesBju7Yl1LBjicT7A7pQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌交易订单表如何做索引优化</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&amp;mid=2650541948&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=99c44ca3235744eeb090fb63c6aa9769&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kW-s-WiZHWtXKBWfz8611g\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kW-s-WiZHWtXKBWfz8611g</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文首先以淘天电商交易订单表线上一条非典型慢 SQL 的深入剖析为切入点，示范如何系统地分析与排查慢 SQL；接着详尽归纳了索引分类、B+Tree 与 B‑Tree 的结构差异、B+Tree 高度估算方法、EXPLAIN 与 Query Profile 等诊断工具的使用，以及索引下推与排序的执行流程等索引优化理论；最后结合日常实践经验，提出了适用于大规模线上集群的索引变更 SOP，并总结了常见的慢 SQL 成因与相应的解决策略。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968348\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.879\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1000\" width=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ec98e5d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TRia2ib69CurGVFVGkGDUoxQuITEdvbad7Ubc413mDiciayspj0ok9BgnqS7icCUic9zb0CHNKEic5EjBKw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌转转UI自动化走查方案探索</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU0OTExNzYwNg==&amp;mid=2247504532&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=498ca0b946fc9c5a43cc8efdd4745e64&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/EJUrFxC_mS6WCWx1xf3KcA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/EJUrFxC_mS6WCWx1xf3KcA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文探讨了将UI自动化走查融入前端开发流程的方案，提出通过前端DOM与设计稿JSON的归一化对比来提升UI还原度与走查效率，比较了叠图、像素、前端节点比对等方案的优劣，最终侧重于基于前端与UI节点数据的结构化对比，并给出数据归一化、边距处理、行高对齐、Padding合并、Mask处理等关键实现要点，以实现高效、可量化的UI走查流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968350\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47314814814814815\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3127349e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TRia2ib69CurGVFVGkGDUoxQZztmeDNwzP0UQmquTRZXe3fUYib7zltBGib4VRthLxnwYdafW5Jg5xGA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"margin: 24px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 48px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-cropsely2=\"65\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\