14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">：从单张图片中重建物体的3D形状、纹理和布局</span></span></li>\n    <li><strong><span leaf=\"\">SAM 3D Body</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">：从单张图片中恢复人体的完整三维姿态与体型</span></span></li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">该模型能够从单张RGB图像中估计人体的完整三维姿态与表面网格（mesh），并在多种自然场景下展现出强大的鲁棒性与泛化能力。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968351\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4925925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1920\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=69a6fcdd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2TRia2ib69CurGVFVGkGDUoxQBxzKYBkxnQuAkQcatX3Bdox2gZApEhzPl9YY8O2XfljEicblcDDT2yQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 48px 8px 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-cropsely2=\"65\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 65px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b74e1aca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoloQt5Gibu37EDyzwasmLC9Ld1Z8ia20TCibPO3Vjh9BB9sKKsPwq4k26g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n   <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:justify;\"><ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Falisdw05xc4frmep\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard></h2>\n   <h2 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌Snow Shot：超好用的截图工具</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://snowshot.top/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://snowshot.top/index.html</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Snow Shot 追求简单高效的使用体验，希望每个用户都能依照直觉无痛使用。本指南将帮助您快速掌握 Snow Shot 的核心功能和使用技巧。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968352\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5268518518518519\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"2062\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7299340f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2TRia2ib69CurGVFVGkGDUoxQXApfsU8eiboicKUXUclZHpFBic2Z1JHS6UgewicWUVgs2ViaucibbbqcVeTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:48px 8px 0em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-cropsely2=\"65\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;height: 65px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d8a4b282&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoQrLTibmRJELUQysO80354ouUOACwWDCCr0NXNjicZbicDGqrqvPSHdibicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n   <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:justify;\"><ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Falisdw05xc4frmep\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard></h2>\n   <h2 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌这个采访有点意思</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwOTU2NzM0NQ==&amp;mid=2247492856&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=075d6dac13091f4a2ab202f25c5da83f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/pWnGzXIybZ0ikQ-_Wz8zNA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/pWnGzXIybZ0ikQ-_Wz8zNA</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文以对北大教授卢锋的访谈为核心，聚焦中国消费疲软的结构性原因、公共资源分配与社会保障改革对消费的影响，以及在新一轮改革中将消费提升纳入发展目标的可行性。作者通过卢锋的观点，分析收入分配、社保与户籍制度等结构性因素如何制约消费与需求，提出以公共资源向消费领域倾斜、改进社会保障体系、优化资源配置以及顶层设计推动改革，以实现经济再平衡和更平稳的增长。</span></span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌面试官都会问为什么辞职这个问题</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5Nzc3MzkyNw==&amp;mid=2247495802&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b2b00b322e2e30dd91289ff271b1bf6f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8YEhZ6Cpo-QPC90axdG0Rg\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8YEhZ6Cpo-QPC90axdG0Rg</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其实面试官问这个问题，目的并不是单纯想听你离开的原因。他们是想通过你离开的原因，来判断你对于工作的需求，对公司的看法，是否符合公司招工的要求，以此来判断你是否能适应新的公司。</span></span></p>\n   <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"hack\" data-id=\"hack\">\n     <div data-support=\"96编辑器\" data-style-id=\"31634\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 48px 0px 10px;\">\n       <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n        <div style=\"width:20%;color:#77af51;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:12px;\" data-width=\"20%\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0px 10px;\">\n          <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">END</span></strong></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本周刊精选并汇总了近期人工智能、软件编程、产品设计等领域的优质技术文章、工具与行业洞察。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本周刊精选并汇总了近期人工智能、软件编程、产品设计等领域的优质技术文章、工具与行业洞察。",
  "summary": "《有意思小周刊 No.156》是一份精心策划的周刊，旨在为技术从业者提供一周内的阅读与思考内容梳理。文章通过简要的摘要和链接，聚合了包括货拉拉大模型应用、AI Agent 框架总结、UI 设计体系、数据库索引优化等多个热门技术领域的推荐阅读。此外，还介绍了 Meta AI 的 3D 模型新发现、实用的截图工具以及对经济和职业发展的深度访谈。周刊的核心价值在于帮助读者高效筛选信息，快速了解行业前沿动态和实用资源，构建个人知识体系，但其本身主要以内容聚合为主，原创深度有限。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "提供精选技术内容聚合，高效节省读者信息筛选时间。",
      "explanation": "周刊通过人工筛选和简要总结，帮助技术从业者快速了解行业热点和优质文章，提高信息获取效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "覆盖人工智能、软件编程等多个热门技术领域，内容广泛。",
      "explanation": "内容涵盖大模型应用、AI Agent 框架、软件架构、UI 设计等，满足不同技术方向读者的多元化需求。"
    },
    {
      "point": "结合实用工具与行业洞察，提供多维度价值参考。",
      "explanation": "除了技术文章，还推荐实用工具和行业专家观点，拓宽读者视野，提供学习和职业发展的参考。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "「有意思小周刊」是我利用零碎时间，梳理记录一周的日常阅读与思考内容。",
    "货拉拉基于大模型的应用开发平台悟空，聚焦功能拓界与业务赋能，以实现大模型在企业级场景中的高效、可控落地。",
    "货拉拉数据工厂在实现 3k+工具、日均超 50 万次调用的规模基础上，通过引入 AI 智能体实现\"所想即所得、所造皆能成\"的转型。",
    "本文系统梳理和对比了当前主流的智能体框架及其设计思路，聚焦于 AutoGen、AgentScope、CAMEL 和 LangGraph 四大框架的核心理念、架构特点、优势与局限。"
  ],
